Params: {3: 'Luna is standing alone in the entrance of the Venus Splash Park, looking at the beach. Gradually, she opens her mouth.'}
{1: '1', 3: 'As if on cue, Roland hops down from a nearby building. His once-damaged frame seems to have been perfunctorily repaired.'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Should we deal with the Babylonians next? I am ready always.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Babylonia playing sleuth here is just helping us clean up.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'They provide a good laugh, so let them be. Let them amuse us.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'While the two are talking, Alpha connects in.'}
{3: 'Roland can see Alpha frowning slightly through the holographic screen.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: 'Just ran into some trouble on the way over.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "No matter. I'll wait for you at the beach.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Luna disconnects and turns to look at Roland.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Gabriel is almost finished on his end. Go meet him.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'With that, Luna leaves, heading to her agreed location with Alpha. Roland, for some reason, is standing still.'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "Miss Luna's expression... Is it just me?", 4: '1'}
